      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WAIKARE ADRIENNA (6) did a great job at her latest appearance at Kilmore, drawing one spot wider than this and racing parked but fighting well to be beaten only a nose into second. Owns a solid record at this circuit and distance. Big chance to go one better. FRANKYTHEFRENCHMAN (4) is working towards a win. Produced a strong effort last start when he led from wider and battled on well for a 1.3m second at Shepparton. Race fit now and can take advantage of this nice draw. I AM HARRO (8) was a Shepparton winner three back and didn't do a bad job for fourth from this row at that same venue last time out. CHARLIE WALKER (7) is heading the right way, improving last time out to finish third from the second line at Melton.",
